 “Dark And Darker”服务器遭受大规模 DDoS 攻击https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-servers-targeted-by-a-titanic-ddos-attack-3495233?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dark-and-darker-服务器遭受泰坦尼克号 DDoS 攻击Imogen DonovanFri, 08 Sep 2023 15:17:20 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3495233 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>服务器现已改进，但罪魁祸首尚不清楚</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-servers-targeted-by-a-titanic-ddos-attack-3495233">遭受大规模 DDoS 攻击的“Dark And Darker”服务器</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dark-and-darker-ddos-attack-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dark-and-darker"><em>《Dark And Darker》</em></a> ——在最受欢迎的 PC 游戏中崛起的地下城爬行游戏——于 8 月 8 日遭受了一次巨大的分布式拒绝服务 (DDoS) 攻击。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-future-of-games-done-quick-why-founder-mike-uyamas-exit-is-on-hold-and-whats-next-3490793">Games Done Quick 的未来：为什么创始人 Mike Uyama 的退出被搁置，以及下一步是什么</a></strong></li></ul><p>巧合的是，这次攻击是在游戏最新更新后发起的。 “我们正在经历一场协同的 DDoS 攻击。因此，我们的响应似乎需要额外的调整。因此，维护时间将比预期的要长一些，”开发者<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ironmace">Ironmace</a>在<a href="https://twitter.com/IronmaceGames/status/1699816828036698560" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X 的帖子</a>中解释道。</p><p> DDoS 攻击是通过来自多个来源的异常流量进行的，从而阻止目标有效识别和减轻信息过载。据开发人员称，在这种情况下，攻击超过“600 Gbps”，这对于可能造成的破坏规模来说是巨大的。</p><p>结果， <em>《Dark And Darker》</em>的服务器遭到入侵，导致玩家无法登录游戏。虽然 Ironmace 利用这次攻击作为加强其服务器的机会，但尚不清楚谁是这次攻击的幕后黑手。 </p><figure id="attachment_3480078" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3480078" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3480078" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dark-and-darker-releases-into-early-access-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3480078" class="wp-caption-text"> “黑暗与黑暗”信用：铁锤</figcaption></figure><p>自 2022 年发布以来， <em>《Dark And Darker》</em>一直处于一系列争议的中心。今年早些时候，发行商 Nexon 声称该游戏是根据其自己的项目<em>P3</em>开发的，并且该游戏的前雇员Ironmace 窃取了其知识产权。</p><p> Ironmace 反驳了这些指控，并表示<em>《Dark And Darker》</em>是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-developer-denies-it-stole-assets-and-code-in-making-of-action-rpg-3403275">团队自己的代码的创建以及虚幻引擎资产的包含</a>。然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-developers-office-searched-by-police-over-allegations-of-code-theft-3410189">开发商的办公室遭到突击搜查，</a>以寻找支持 Nexon 案件的证据，并且在发行商发出 DMCA 通知后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-developer-cannot-ignore-being-blackballed-by-steam-3480030">，该游戏已从 Steam 下架</a>。</p><p>这场拉锯战最终在美国华盛顿对 Ironmace 提起了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-playtest-faces-sophisticated-server-ddos-attacks-3432123">版权侵权</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-playtest-faces-sophisticated-server-ddos-attacks-3432123">诉讼</a>，开发商指责 Nexon “[扭曲]版权法，以防止<em>《Dark And Darker》</em>落入公众手中”。</p><p>然而，8 月 17 日，美国华盛顿西区地方法院在没有偏见的情况下驳回了 Nexon 的所有索赔。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>《博德之门 3》</em></a>可能的资料片的大门还没有完全关闭， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-director-talks-about-when-a-dlc-would-be-set-3495142">导演已经在其时间表中提出了一个潜在的设定</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dark-and-darker-servers-targeted-by-a-titanic-ddos-attack-3495233">遭受大规模 DDoS 攻击的“Dark And Darker”服务器</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
